build_mon
---------

This very simple QT4 application shows a fullscreen webkit widget with a
configured url. It can be used to show your monitoring dashboard or the a
buildchain status page.

To compile this application you need qmake and qt4 (apt-get install libqt4-dev
libqt4-webkit qt4-qmake).

https://travis-ci.org/mattthias/build_mon.svg

Run:
        qmake
        make
        ./build_mon

To configure the url shown created a config file $HOME/.config/mattthias/build_mon.ini
```
[build_mon]
url = https://github.com/mattthias/build_mon
```

